    • isEquivalentUnderTransposition

    True if receiver is equivalent to 'pitchSet' under transposition.
    
    Otherwise false.
    
    code::
    a = FoscPitchSet(#[60,61,62]);
    b = FoscPitchSet(#[61,62,63]);
